<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10084927>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Dorycera punctulata sp. n. holotype ♂ (a–e), and ♀ (f, g) genitalia: a—habitus, left lateral view; b—head, left lateral view c—head and mesonotum; d, g—abdomen, dorsal view; e, f —wing; h—labels. Scale bar for e and f = 1 mm. Photos by Valery Korneyev." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10084927/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10084929>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Dorycera punctulata sp. n. paratype ♂ (dissected): a—habitus, left lateral view; b—labels. Scale bar unavailable. Photos by Valery Korneyev." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10084929/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10084931>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Dorycera grisipennis (a, b, e) and D. punctulata sp. n. (c, d. f. g), male (a–f) and female (g) genitalia: a, c— epandrium and surstyli, posterior view (proctiger not shown); b, d—same, lateral left and ventral view; e,f—phallus, partly compressed; f—spermatheca (one of the three). Scale bar unavailable. Figures by H. Ackerman (2012)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10084931/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

